      "name": "Note: OpenRouter Chat Model"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "### All Required Fields Found?\n\nTwo-way gate on `={{ $json.output?.requestId }}`. TRUE continues the happy path, FALSE takes the alternate branch.\n\nPorts: ①→ Upsert into Airtable · ②→ Queue for Manual Review",
